    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The board of public works to-\nmorrow afternoon will take up the\nquestion of grade separation on\nEast Front avenue, near the\nSchade brewery, where a switch of\nthe Northern Pacific crosses that\nthoroughfare. Plans have been\nprepared by City Engineer Ralston\nand any objections to the plans\nwill be considered at the meeting\ntomorrow afternoon."
